"uid":36072,"like":148,"dislike":1,"score":147,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T07:45:50.000Z","msg":"大學有同學個老豆以前揸九巴<br />\n有次傾計講到嚟個問題<br />\n佢話佢老豆果時會帶肛塞返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70466cbac76b4470b015e7fc5bd136a95bb32fc3","tid":797891,"uid":12568,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T07:50:21.000Z","msg":"渣住架新車飛返去總站都仲好<br />\n急屎渣著架大烏龜上斜得20會唔會絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123e4ea3864d9db7f6f9a43f230d84739286c8e8","tid":797891,"uid":170154,"like":107,"dislike":1,"score":106,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"有次係日本啲鄉下嘅地方<br />\n搭搭下巴士,<br />\n司機(後生仔30歲左右)無啦啦係一個唔係巴士站嘅地方停咗車,<br />\n然後講聲唔好意思就衝咗落車跑入去路邊嘅舖頭<br />\n過咗6,7分鐘先返上車<br />\n睇得出佢好唔好意思同心急<br />\n因為佢跑上車個陣仲pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a067b6c57a51302cc5ba4b4b7f04a23e60d525","tid":797891,"uid":84751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"著定屎片咪得囉"},{"pid":"e7493a4ca347a30581935207fae38b944ac86151","tid":797891,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"揸長途車都會包尿片"},{"pid":"9552beb332685cd13c44e1ff032e41ed55289672","tid":797891,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"每渣完一程咪去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔見總站d司機會出去抖既咩"},{"pid":"0e546201efffaf8bf6ccbc3b9caeb4b27e2fce0c","tid":797891,"uid":65074,"like":159,"dislike":1,"score":158,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:20:34.000Z","msg":"中學時代有次黑雨<br />\n搭巴士返屋企<br />\n平時20分鐘到  果日搭左2個幾鐘<br />\n好悶冇野做<br />\n巴士司機請我食餅(咁啱坐車頭)<br />\n講完多謝傾左幾句<br />\n講到我問佢平時你地想去廁所點算<br />\n佢就唔應機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d6867c10affc03c1af85690a7bbd33b0b0a2b0","tid":797891,"uid":153570,"like"